               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 3ra-44va)
 I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-6rb)
 I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 6va-8va)
 I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... "I worship Thee ..." (fols. 8va-9va)
 I-4) Taʾammǝra
                     Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 47 miracles (fols. 9va-44va), incomplete
 II)
                     Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus "Miracles of Jesus" (fols. 45ra-66vb)
 II-1) ʾƎsaggǝd
                     la-malakotǝka ... "I worship Thy Godhead ..." (fols. 45ra-47rb)
 II-2)
                     Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus "Miracles of Jesus": 12 miracles (fols. 47rb-66vb)
 III)
                     Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel Miracles of Michael": 2 miracles (fols. 66vb-68ra)
 IV)
                     Taʾammǝra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus "Miracles of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus": 1 miracle (fol.
                     68ra-vb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
